quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  5,18,"Ne Abayahudi nende Abakiristo baboola mbu, “Efwe khuli abana ba Nyasaye nende abahelwa bebe.” Boola mbu, “Ne shichila shina abahelesinjia eshinyasio khulwetsimbii tsienyu?” Halali, enywe mulisa abandu mubayaloonga; aleshelanga owayenya, ne ahelesinjia eshinyasio wayenya. Ne ni bwa Nyasaye obwami bwomwikulu nende khushialo nende bili hakari wabio. Ne ewuwe butswa niwokhukalukha."
  5,19,"Enywe Abandu beshitabu, toto Omurumwa wefu yamala okhubeetsela, abeenosilie ebise bia abarumwa bandi bawumao; mulakhetsa mwaboola mbu, “Omwikanyilisi nohomba owureranga akomwikhoyo shiyakhwitsila tawe.” Toto yabetsela owureranga akomwikhoyo nende omwikanyilisi. Ne Nyasaye ni Omunyali muno wabuli eshindu."
  5,20,"Ne olwa Musa yaboolela Abandu bebe mbu, “Enywe abandu banje, yitsulile emikabo chia Nyasaye khwinywe, olwa yakhola Abarumwa mwinywe, ne nabakhola enywe okhuba abaami, mana nabahelesia akayalahelesiakhwo yesiyesi mubiloonje bioosi tawe."
  5,21,"Enywe abandu banje, injile mumukunda kwoluyali okwa Nyasaye yabalachila, ne mulakalukha inyuma tawe; mwakalukhana okhuba abokhusikha.""
  5,22,"Baboola mbu, “Ewe Musa, toto eyo abandu baliyo abamakhakha. Ne efwe shikhulenjilayo tawe okhuula baruleyo. Nibarulayo, toto efwe khulenjilayo.""
  5,23,"Abandu babili mubalia abaria emikabo chia Nyasaye khubo baboola mbu, “Benjilile mumuliango kuno, nimumala okhubenjilila, awo toto enywe mulabashila. Ne mwisike Nyasaye, toto nimuli Abasuubili.”"